SUMMARY:Seattle Public Library Behind the Scenes
DESCRIPTION:Jason Davis\, the Greenwood Branch Adult Librarian\, joins us to talk about all of the behind-the-scenes systems that keep Seattle’s libraries running smoothly. Come learn about all the steps that occur when you request a hold\, how interlibrary loans travel around\, how extensive the collection really is\, how books are selected for different branches\, what’s in the special collections\, and more! RSVP: 206.297.0875
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/seattle-public-library-behind-the-scenes/
LOCATION:Greenwood Senior Center\, 525 N. 85th St.\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
